div.p:
Off Turn Point, on Stuart Island, there are strong whirls and eddy tides;
                        and, unless with a commanding breeze, a sailing-vessel is liable to be
                        turned round by them and lose the power of her helm.

My age is fifty-eight years; my residence, Victoria, Vancouver Island,
                            and have resided here since the year eighteen hundred and fifty-eight;
                            my occupation is that of merchant.
